category=Building an Application using Objects
description=<p>Applications often need to make decisions.  This tutorial introduces you to using 'if...then' to run different scripts depending on the outcome of a decision.  We go on to take a look at using switch to choose from a list of possible decisions.</p>
duration=6:41
filename=free_if-then-else_and_switch.avi
level=1
licensed=false
name=If...then...else and Switch
scripts=<p><font face="Tahoma" size="11" color="#000000">Scripts Used in this Tutorial:</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  answer &quot;Do you want the computer to beep?&quot; with &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Yes&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  if it is &quot;Yes&quot; then beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  answer &quot;Do you want the computer to beep?&quot; with &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Yes&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  if it is &quot;Yes&quot; then beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  else answer &quot;OK Then.&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  answer &quot;Do you want the computer to beep?&quot; with &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Yes&quot; \\</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    or &quot;Perhaps&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  if it is &quot;Yes&quot; then beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  else if it is &quot;No&quot; then answer &quot;OK Then.&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  else if it is &quot;Perhaps&quot; and the random of 2 is 1 then beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  answer &quot;Do you want the computer to beep?&quot; with &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Yes&quot; \\</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    or &quot;Perhaps&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  if it is &quot;Yes&quot; then</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;Yes&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  else if it is &quot;No&quot; then</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    answer &quot;OK Then.&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;No&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  else if it is &quot;Perhaps&quot; and the random of 2 is 1 then</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;Perhaps&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  end if</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  answer &quot;Do you want the computer to beep?&quot; with &quot;No&quot; or &quot;Yes&quot; \\</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    or &quot;Perhaps&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  switch it</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">     case &quot;Yes&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">       beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">       --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;Yes&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">     exit switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">     case &quot;No&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">       answer &quot;OK Then.&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">       --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;No&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">     exit switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">     case &quot;Perhaps&quot; </font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">        if the random of 2 is 1 then beep</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">        --you can insert additional script lines here for &quot;Perhaps&quot;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">    exit switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">  end switch</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" size="12" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>
title=If...then...else and switch: how an application makes a decision.
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;Making choices using 'if...then...else'</p>\n<p>-&#9;Making more complex choices using 'switch&#133;case'</p>\n<p>-&#9;Making a random choice</p>\n<p>-&#9;Using comments in scripts</p>\n<p></p>